<br>
*shakes head in disgust*<br>
The only way to solve these problems is if more people join and form one team guilds that are aggressive.  It is the only way you can destroy the light alliance.  The only way you can ensure that alliances between teams are not formed.  It is the ONLY way you can ensure that PvP stays alive.<br>
<br>
However, I know many of you will not choose this road.  Mostly because you are weak.  You want to choose the easy way out, instead of standing up for what is right, instead of fighting for what SHOULD BE yours.  You are weak bluebies.  You may deny it all you want, but in the end it is true.  <br>
<br>
