<br>
Lets assume now, that PDM is able to stick to their guns and keep their guild fighting against everyone else.  Rival guilds will form, they may or not be allied.  PDM may start to lose members to those guilds.  (Go back up and read the thing about friends.)  PDM's moral will begin to decline, and you will see a domino effect of friends going to join friends in GuildX.  And if you lose a important member, may the gods help you, moral will come crashing down and you will see tons of members who looked up to that member flocking behind him/her.<br>
<br>
